title: Match of the Day 2 - S10E01 - 9th August 2015 - 720p x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day 2
On: BBC 1 HD    
Date: Sunday 9th August 2015 
Time: 22:30 to 23:40 

Highlights and analysis of the day's three Premier League matches, plus a round-up of Saturday's action, introduced by Mark Chapman. Arsenal have approached the new season in confident mood after ending the last campaign strongly and retaining the FA Cup. Sunday's opponents West Ham haven't beaten the Gunners in 15 attempts, but their new manager Slaven Bilic has been backed in the transfer market and set a target of a top-eight finish by the club's owners. There is a managerial bow too for Steve McClaren at Newcastle, who host Southampton, while Stoke City face Liverpool in a repeat of the final day of last season, when the Potters scored five first-half goals as Brendan Rodgers' side were thrashed 6-1.
